mg alt=\"Bill-guisarme.png\" src=\"/images/5/5d/Bill-guisarme.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>草铁长柄锲\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td>带钩长柄武器\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（小型）\n</th>\n<td>2d4\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（大型）\n</th>\n<td>d10\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>命中修正\n</th>\n<td>+0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>武器技能类别\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>规格\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"双手 (page does not exist)\">双手</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>7 <a href=\"/wiki/Zm/zh-CN\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm/zh-CN\">zm</a><br />（+10/正数附魔等级）\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">120</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i>“倒勾刀”、“弯曲长柄武器”重定向至此。</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>草铁长柄锲</b>（bill-guisarme）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"武器\">武器</a>。它是一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>，由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时外观为<b>带钩长柄武器</b>（hooked polearm）。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#dNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">dNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#NetHack_Fourk\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">NetHack Fourk</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#xNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">xNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#EvilHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">EvilHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%AD%A6%E5%8D%AB%E5%91%98&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"警卫员 (page does not exist)\">警卫员</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"士兵 (page does not exist)\">士兵</a>在生成时有概率<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物起始物品 (page does not exist)\">携带</a>草铁长柄锲<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>草铁长柄锲的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">重量</a>在长柄武器中与<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E6%96%A7\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"大战斧\">大战斧</a>并列第三。它对<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"小型 (page does not exist)\">小型</a>怪物的伤害在长柄武器中较高，对大型怪物的伤害也不错。不过，<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%8B%E9%92%AF\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"镋钯\">镋钯</a>造成的伤害也不差，而且重量只有草铁长柄锲的<sup>2</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>草铁长柄锲最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_1.3d\" title=\"NetHack 1.3d\">NetHack 1.3d</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bill_(weapon)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Bill (weapon)\">Bill (weapon)</a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Bill-guisarmes.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/Bill-guisarmes.png/150px-Bill-guisarmes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"135\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/b/bf/Bill-guisarmes.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Bill-guisarmes.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>草铁长柄锲</div></div></div>\n<p>草铁长柄锲的英文名称中的“bill”（也称“billhook”）是一种修枝用的农具，其外观近似于柴刀。在中世纪欧洲，它和其他一些农具一样被改造成各种长柄武器，工匠们在锲的刀刃上加装多种凸出的刀刃，草铁长柄锲就是其中一种类型。长柄锲的外观、大小和功能近似于<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%96%A7%E6%9E%AA\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"斧枪\">斧枪</a>，其外形演变反映了长柄武器发展过程中在设计上的趋同演化。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Bill-guisarme/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"dNetHack\">dNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack\" title=\"DNetHack\">dNetHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/NotdNetHack\" title=\"NotdNetHack\">notdNetHack</a>, the bill-guisarme has its weight reduced to 80 aum, the same as the guisarme.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"NetHack_Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_Fourk\" title=\"NetHack Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</a> removes the bill-guisarme and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"xNetHack\">xNetHack</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/XNetHack\" title=\"XNetHack\">xNetHack</a> removes the bill-guisarme and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>, a bill-guisarme can be created at a <a href=\"/wiki/Forge_(dungeon_feature)\" title=\"Forge (dungeon feature)\">forge</a> by combining a guisarme and a <a href=\"/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\">spear</a>. This also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>请参阅<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器的百科文本</a>。</i></dd></dl>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L194\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 194</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182552\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.053 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 435/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2682/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4794/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 747/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip 