ef=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:General_disclaimer\" title=\"NetHackWiki:General disclaimer\">Disclaimers</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"footer-icons\" class=\"noprint\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"footer-poweredbyico\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"//www.mediawiki.org/\"><img src=\"/resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_88x31.png\" alt=\"Powered by MediaWiki\" srcset=\"/resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_132x47.png 1.5x, /resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_176x62.png 2x\" width=\"88\" height=\"31\"/></a>\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.037\",\"walltime\":\"0.053\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":435,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":2682,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":4794,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":747,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":9,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":4,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":448,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   36.134      1 -total\",\" 21.01%    7.593      1 Template:Languages\",\" 17.45%    6.307      1 Template:Refsrc\",\" 14.73%    5.323      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\",\" 14.18%    5.123      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\" 12.19%    4.405      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\",\" 10.29%    3.718      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\",\"  8.93%    3.227      1 Template:Wikipedia/zh-CN\",\"  5.93%    2.142      1 Template:Top_icon\",\"  5.52%    1.994      1 Template:Refsrc/link\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926182552\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":93});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{weapon/zh-CN\n |name=草铁长柄锲\n |tile=[[image:bill-guisarme.png]]\n |appearance=带钩长柄武器\n |smalldmg=2d4\n |largedmg=d10\n |tohit=<nowiki>+0</nowiki>\n |skill=长柄武器\n |size=双手\n |cost=7\n |weight=120\n |material=铁\n}}\n\n{{redirects-here/zh-CN|倒勾刀|弯曲长柄武器}}\n\n'''草铁长柄锲'''（bill-guisarme）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[武器]]。它是一种[[长柄武器]]，由[[铁]]制成，未[[鉴定]]时外观为'''带钩长柄武器'''（hooked polearm）。\n\n== 生成 ==\n[[警卫员]]和[[士兵]]在生成时有概率[[怪物起始物品|携带]]草铁长柄锲{{refsrc|src/makemon.c|194|version=NetHack 3.6.7}}。\n\n== 策略 ==\n草铁长柄锲的[[重量]]在长柄武器中与[[大战斧]]并列第三。它对[[小型]]怪物的伤害在长柄武器中较高，对大型怪物的伤害也不错。不过，[[镋钯]]造成的伤害也不差，而且重量只有草铁长柄锲的{{frac|2|5}}。\n\n== 历史 ==\n草铁长柄锲最初于[[NetHack 1.3d]]加入游戏。\n\n== 起源 ==\n{{wikipedia/zh-CN|Bill (weapon)}}\n[[Image:Bill-guisarmes.png|150px|thumb|right|草铁长柄锲]]\n草铁长柄锲的英文名称中的“bill”（也称“billhook”）是一种修枝用的农具，其外观近似于柴刀。在中世纪欧洲，它和其他一些农具一样被改造成各种长柄武器，工匠们在锲的刀刃上加装多种凸出的刀刃，草铁长柄锲就是其中一种类型。长柄锲的外观、大小和功能近似于[[斧枪]]，其外形演变反映了长柄武器发展过程中在设计上的趋同演化。\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\n===dNetHack===\nIn [[dNetHack]] and [[notdNetHack]], the bill-guisarme has its weight reduced to 80 aum, the same as the guisarme.\n\n===NetHack Fourk===\n[[NetHack Fourk]] removes the bill-guisarme and many other polearms.\n\n===xNetHack===\n[[xNetHack]] removes the bill-guisarme and many other polearms.\n\n===EvilHack===\nIn [[EvilHack]], a bill-guisarme can be created at a [[Forge (dungeon feature)|forge]] by combining a guisarme and a [[spear]]. This also applies to [[Hack'EM]].\n\n== 百科文本 ==\n{{encyclopedia-redirect/zh-CN|长柄武器}}\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Weapons/zh-CN|CAOTIECHANGBINGQIE]]"}